title: Mapping corrections to Grimrail Depot, Iron Docks and Tazavesh: So'leah's Gambit & Shrouded enemies now give enemy forces

changes.change: Grimrail Depot now has enemy forces and Inspiring enemies mapped (Shrouded was already done).
Iron Docks now has all Shrouded and Inspiring enemies mapped. Some enemy forces are still missing after first boss.
Tazavesh: So'leah's Gambit now has all Shrouded enemies mapped.
Nathrezim Infiltrators now give 6 enemy forces - Zul'gamux 18
